# Testing

**Authoritative source:** [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md) §5↔§7 (commands, pre-PR checklist). **`AGENTS.md` wins** on any conflict.

## Commands

- From monorepo root: **`pnpm test`** (Turborepo / per-package tasks) → see **`AGENTS.md` §6**.
- Prefer the **same runner and patterns** as the package under test (Vitest, Jest, Playwright, etc.) → copy import and setup style from neighboring test files.

## Honesty & quality

- **Never fabricate** test results, logs, or command output; state uncertainty explicitly (**`AGENTS.md` §5**).
- **Pre-PR:** all tests pass before merge (**`AGENTS.md` §7**); if tests cannot be run in the current environment, say so and list what was verified.

## Structure

- **Colocate** tests with source using the repo's convention (`*.test.ts`, `__tests__/`, `e2e/`, etc.).
- **Mocks:** mock **I/O and external services**, not safety-critical validation, unless an existing pattern does so → follow package precedent.
- **PII:** use synthetic fixtures only; never real patient data (**`AGENTS.md` §5**).

## Healthcare / security

- For healthcare apps, **`pnpm security:primary-healthcare`** may be required before PRs → see **`AGENTS.md` §6↔§7**.

## Gold standard references

- Follow test patterns in `@packages/iskandar-gatekeeper/src/__tests__/auth.test.ts`.
- Follow e2e patterns in `@apps/platform/sentra-portal/e2e/smoke.spec.ts`.

